;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">To jedyne miejsce, gdzie dozwolone są jakiekolwiek prace potencjalnie „brudne”.&nbsp;</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:6pt;"><span style="font-size:13.999999999999998pt;font-family:Ubuntu,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">PPNT (Budynek II):</span><span style="font-size:13.999999999999998pt;font-family:Ubuntu,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;"> Sala Piaskowa</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:6pt;"><span style="font-size:13.999999999999998pt;font-family:Ubuntu,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">PPNT (Budynek III):</span><span style="font-size:13.999999999999998pt;font-family:Ubuntu,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;"> Sala G (na I piętrze)</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3800000000000001;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:6pt;"><span style="font-size:13.999999999999998pt;font-family:Ubuntu,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Arena:</span><span style="font-size:13.999999999999998pt;font-family:Ubuntu,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoratio